            {/* Placeholder for more specific info on contributors, core team, or how to find active members, e.g., on Matrix or GitHub */}
            We are a do-ocracy. The best way to see who is involved is to join our community channels and see who is building!
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <a href="/community" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg text-lg transition duration-300">Meet the Community</a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

